Recommends: python3-anthropic
Suggests: ollama
Description: AI-enhanced terminal shell
 AgentSH is an AI-enhanced terminal shell that understands natural language
 commands and translates them into shell commands. It provides:
 .
  - Natural language to command translation
  - Multi-provider LLM support (Anthropic, OpenAI, Ollama, OpenRouter)
  - Context-aware command generation
  - Safe command execution with confirmation
  - Full PTY support for interactive programs
  - Bash/Zsh/Fish compatible
 .
 This package provides the agentsh command and can be set as a login shell.
